{"name":"Save applications with Airtable and Outlook","nodes":[{"parameters":{"formTitle":"Save applications with Airtable and Outlook","formFields":{"values":[{"fieldLabel":"From","requiredField":true},{"fieldLabel":"Subject","requiredField":false},{"fieldLabel":"Receivedat","requiredField":false}]},"options":{"appendAttribution":false}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.formTrigger","typeVersion":2.2,"position":[-270,400],"id":"9b183779-eabb-4aaa-a4c2-e2b253f9cbab","name":"New Email Form Submission","webhookId":"4dc141cd-67f4-487d-9290-f02615d31edc"},{"parameters":{"mode":"runOnceForAllItems","jsCode":"// Normalize incoming email records to a stable schema\nconst out = [];\nfor (const item of $input.all()) {\n  const j = item.json;\n  out.push({ json: {\n    messageId: String(j.messageId ?? j.id ?? '').trim(),\n    from: typeof j.from === 'string' ? j.from.trim() : j.from ?? null,\n    source: j.source ?? 'api',\n    receivedAt: new Date().toISOString(),\n  } });\n}\nreturn out;"},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.code","typeVersion":2,"position":[54,400],"id":"b2f973fc-0fc1-424b-b44d-bbd38be4f780","name":"Normalize Email Payload"},{"parameters":{"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"cc654a8e-ed58-49b4-b790-21766ff2b367","name":"requestId","value":"={{ $json.messageId || $execution.id }}","type":"string"},{"id":"45a966fa-a01f-47c0-aabd-37dfb75bcdca","name":"summary","value":"={{ ($json.from || '').toString().slice(0, 200) }}","type":"string"},{"id":"763d0257-023e-4a50-82ba-9e22566ef1c7","name":"requestedBy","value":"={{ $json.email || 'system' }}","type":"string"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[378,400],"id":"f9c89d0e-e88d-4298-b428-f670b5e0b338","name":"Prepare Approval Packet"},{"parameters":{"select":"channel","channelId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"#inbox-ops","cachedResultName":"#inbox-ops"},"text":"=🟡 Approval needed for {{ $json.summary }} — resume link: {{ $execution.resumeUrl }}","otherOptions":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.slack"